public enum SubscriptionType
extends java.lang.Enum<SubscriptionType>

Values for the 'type' attribute of presences, taken from RFC3921. These are only types from stanzas dealing with subscriptiosn. Types used for presence information are enumerated in PresenceType even though they are both communicated via presence stanzas.
